 target=\"_blank\">http://thehill.com/homenews/house/389571-more-than-60-dem-lawmakers-demand-ethics-investigation-into-trumps</a><br />\n<br />\nRep. David Cicilline (D-R.I.) posted a letter to David Apol, acting head of the federal government's ethics office, to Twitter on Sunday, stating that the request was prompted by Trump &quot;advocating&quot; for ZTE just days after the Chinese government gave one of the president's business endeavors a $500 million loan.<br />\n<br />\nIn the letter, lawmakers say the business dealing between the Trump Organization and China may have violated U.S. laws forbidding public officials from accepting payments or gifts from foreign entities without Congress's approval."},{"pid":"150d7f029bbacdefcbcbdd9108e700dc3c5e59eb","tid":682828,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0bcf5d94fb00b6336cb3d6dfa140b561ea0ff4f","tid":682828,"uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2cfeae5a9c9972ce6888147df202e7ecd54367a0","tid":682828,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ecd56e620a082b1ffb9ffeb4179ef886be1e3e8b","tid":682828,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"侵侵只係對贏國人既生死無感覺姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"等睇佢對香港人死都冇感覺<br />\n<br />\n都唔明愛侵力會覺得呢條仆街會幫香港？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:54:46.000Z","msg":"佢肯唔再養支那, 已經足夠"},{"pid":"089e974c331f8221a7548e382bd95e2b9035aced","tid":682828,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f077405e0fae2ca0675fd8aa299e4078551b6c5","tid":682828,"uid":84392,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"認真講<br />\n64同UR 完全唔同<br />\n佢都知咩事"}]}